n style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">)</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 1;\"><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-yfti-cnfc: 4;\"><b><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">Prior sPTB or short cervical length (&lt;20 mm)</span></b></p></td><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">Vaginal suppositories#</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">100 mg vaginal suppository every night</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">(</span><a title=\"da Fonseca, 2003 #184\" href=\"#_ENREF_5\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191; mso-no-proof: yes; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">da Fonseca et al., 2003</span></a><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">)</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 2;\"><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; background: silver; mso-background-themecolor: text1; mso-background-themetint: 63; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-yfti-cnfc: 68;\"><b><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">Prior sPTB or short cervical length (&lt;20 MM)</span></b></p></td><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; background: silver; mso-background-themecolor: text1; mso-background-themetint: 63; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-yfti-cnfc: 64;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">Micronized capsules</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">â€ </span></p></td><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; background: silver; mso-background-themecolor: text1; mso-background-themetint: 63; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-yfti-cnfc: 64;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\">200 mg vaginally daily</span></p></td><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; background: silver; mso-background-themecolor: text1; mso-background-themetint: 63; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-yfti-cnfc: 64;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191;\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">(</span><a title=\"Fonseca, 2007 #185\" href=\"#_ENREF_6\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themeshade: 191; mso-no-proof: yes; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">Fonseca et al., 2007</span></a><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">)</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 3; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes;\"><td style=\"width: 119.7pt; border: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; mso-border-bottom-themecolor: text1; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-hei