nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"