f=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<!--   TD   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD2\">\r\n         <p>   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD3\">\r\n         <p>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD4\">\r\n         <p>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD5\">\r\n         <p>  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-14 23:57:40','2013-08-15 04:57:40','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-92/',0,'revision','',0),(512,5,'2013-08-14 23:59:10','2013-08-15 04:59:10','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n   \n\n\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SLE   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n \n\n<!--   TD - Thyroid Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD2\">\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to               \n                    conception for normal fetal development. Iodine                                                                                  considered safe.\n                    intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD3\">\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD4\">\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD5\">\n         <p>  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-14 23:59:10','2013-08-15 04:59:10','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-93/',0,'revision','',0),(513,5,'2013-08-15 00:00:27','2013-08-15 05:00:27','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n   \n\n\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SLE   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n \n\n<!--   TD - Thyroid Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD2\">\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD3\">\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD4\">\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD5\">\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:00:27','2013-08-15 05:00:27','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-94/',0,'revision','',0),(514,5,'2013-08-15 00:01:37','2013-08-15 05:01:37','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n   \n\n\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SLE   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n \n\n<!--   TD - Thyroid Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD2\">\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD3\">\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD4\">\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTD5\">\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:01:37','2013-08-15 05:01:37','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-95/',0,'revision','',0),(515,5,'2013-08-15 00:01:54','2013-08-15 05:01:54','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<!--   TD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:01:54','2013-08-15 05:01:54','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-96/',0,'revision','',0),(516,5,'2013-08-15 00:03:33','2013-08-15 05:03:33','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:03:33','2013-08-15 05:03:33','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-97/',0,'revision','',0),(517,5,'2013-08-15 00:06:24','2013-08-15 05:06:24','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n   \n\n\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SLE   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   TRD   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\n         <p>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\n         <p>  </p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:06:24','2013-08-15 05:06:24','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-98/',0,'revision','',0),(518,5,'2013-08-15 00:06:57','2013-08-15 05:06:57','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:06:57','2013-08-15 05:06:57','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-99/',0,'revision','',0),(519,5,'2013-08-15 00:08:10','2013-08-15 05:08:10','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n   \n\n\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SLE   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   TRD   --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€ http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us\n ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\n           This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013\n','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:08:10','2013-08-15 05:08:10','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-100/',0,'revision','',0),(520,5,'2013-08-15 00:08:56','2013-08-15 05:08:56','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€ <a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013\r\n','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:08:56','2013-08-15 05:08:56','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-101/',0,'revision','',0),(521,5,'2013-08-15 00:09:08','2013-08-15 05:09:08','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013\r\n','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:09:08','2013-08-15 05:09:08','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-102/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (524,5,'2013-08-15 00:10:34','2013-08-15 05:10:34','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:10:34','2013-08-15 05:10:34','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-105/',0,'revision','',0),(522,5,'2013-08-15 00:10:04','2013-08-15 05:10:04','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:10:04','2013-08-15 05:10:04','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-103/',0,'revision','',0),(523,5,'2013-08-15 00:10:19','2013-08-15 05:10:19','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1\r\n                    month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:10:19','2013-08-15 05:10:19','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-104/',0,'revision','',0),(525,5,'2013-08-15 00:11:06','2013-08-15 05:11:06','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"Rheumatoid Arthritis\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:11:06','2013-08-15 05:11:06','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-106/',0,'revision','',0),(526,5,'2013-08-15 00:11:41','2013-08-15 05:11:41','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"Rheumatoid Arthritis\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:11:41','2013-08-15 05:11:41','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-107/',0,'revision','',0),(527,5,'2013-08-15 00:12:03','2013-08-15 05:12:03','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \r\n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"Rheumatoid Arthritis\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:12:03','2013-08-15 05:12:03','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-108/',0,'revision','',0),(528,5,'2013-08-15 00:13:58','2013-08-15 05:13:58','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 <a href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html\" target=\"_blank\">http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \r\n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"Rheumatoid Arthritis\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity </a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:13:58','2013-08-15 05:13:58','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-109/',0,'revision','',0),(532,5,'2013-08-15 09:22:02','2013-08-15 14:22:02','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 <a href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html\" target=\"_blank\">http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \r\n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€ \r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 09:22:02','2013-08-15 14:22:02','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-113/',0,'revision','',0),(529,5,'2013-08-15 00:17:49','2013-08-15 05:17:49','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 <a href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html\" target=\"_blank\">http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \r\n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:17:49','2013-08-15 05:17:49','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-110/',0,'revision','',0),(531,5,'2013-08-15 00:19:33','2013-08-15 05:19:33','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 <a href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html\" target=\"_blank\">http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \r\n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€ \r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:19:33','2013-08-15 05:19:33','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-112/',0,'revision','',0),(530,5,'2013-08-15 00:18:46','2013-08-15 05:18:46','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\r\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\r\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n   \r\n\r\n\r\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\r\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\r\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\r\n         <p>None </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\r\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\r\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\r\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\r\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\r\n \r\n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\r\n      <p> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\r\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 <a href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html\" target=\"_blank\">http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\r\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\r\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\r\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--    HIV  --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\r\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\r\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\r\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\r\n \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\r\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\r\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \r\n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\r\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\r\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\r\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity</a></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\r\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\r\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\r\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\r\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\r\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\r\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\r\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\r\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\r\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\r\n \r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\r\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\r\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\r\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\r\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\r\n   \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\r\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\r\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\r\n    </p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\r\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\r\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\r\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n<!--   TRD   --->\r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\r\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\r\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\r\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\r\n   </ul>\r\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\r\n      \r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\r\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\r\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\r\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\r\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\r\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\r\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\r\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\r\n\r\n\r\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€\r\n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Us  ing_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\r\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 00:18:46','2013-08-15 05:18:46','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-111/',0,'revision','',0),(547,5,'2013-08-15 11:04:42','2013-08-15 16:04:42','<!--  AS - Asthma   -->\n<div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabAS1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Asthma</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabAS5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabAS1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAs4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabAS5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabAS5 -->\n</div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n   \n\n\n<!--     CD - Cardiovascular Disease  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabCD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Cardiovascular Disease</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabCD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabCD1\">\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD2\">\n         <p>Women with poor control of their asthma should use contraception until it is well controlled</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD3\">\n         <p>See NHLBI Guidelines for Diagnosis and Management of Asthma <a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD4\">\n         <p>None </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabCD5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabCD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    DE - Depression  --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Depression </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDE1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE2\">\n        <p>Screening prior to pregnancy allows for treatment and control of symptoms that may help prevent negative pregnancy and family outcomes.</p>   \n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE3\">\n         <p>See NIMH Women and Depression: Discovering Hope <a href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml \" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/publications/women-and-depression-discovering-hope/how-is-depression-diagnosed-and-treated.shtml </a> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE4\">\n        <p> Paroxetine   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDE5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe</p>\n    </div> <!-- end of tabDE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   DI -  Diabetes  --->\n \n <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabDI1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Diabetes</strong> </a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabDI5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabDI1\">\n      <p> </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI2\">\n         <p>Hyperglycemia during the first trimester is a risk  factor for abnormal fetal organogenesis. Stress the importance of euglycemic control before   pregnancy. Convert women on oral agents to insulin before conception. High risk for neural tube defect: instruct them to take multivitamin with 400 Î¼g of folic acid before conception. protein and creatinine clearance, thyroid function tests, and an ECG. See ADA Standards of Medical Care in Diabetes 2012 <a href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html\" target=\"_blank\">http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/35/Supplement_1/S4.full.pdf+html</a></p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI3\">\n         <p>Evidence of good glycemic control: HgbA1c < 6.5. On select women: examine for underlying vasculopathy: retinal exam by an ophthalmologist, 24-hour urine for</p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI4\">\n         <p>ACE Inhibitors,  Statins</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabDI5\">\n         <p>Avoid: estrogen containing methods  in some women. See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabDI5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--    HIV  --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHIV1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>HIV </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHIV5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHIV1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV2\">\n         <p>HIV may be life-threatening to the infant if   transmitted. Antiretroviral therapy can reduce  the risk of transmission but the risk is still ~2%.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV3\">\n         <p>Refer to subspecialist. See guidelines for treatment: <a href=\"http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aidsinfo.nih.gov/guidelines/</a>  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV4\">\n         <p>Efavienz (SustivaÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHIV5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.</p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHIV5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   HY  - Hypertension --->\n \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabHY1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Hypertension</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabHY5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabHY1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY2\">\n         <p> Increased maternal and fetal risk during pregnancy, especially for pre-eclampsia. Discuss importance of finding alternative to ACE inhibitor prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY3\">\n         <p>Women with HTN for several years should be  assessed for ventricular hypertrophy, retinopathy and renal disease. Consult with a cardiac specialist. See  NHLBI Seventh Report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation,  and Treatment of High Blood Pressure (JNC 7 Express) \n<a href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/hypertension/jncintro.htm</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabHY5\">\n         <p> Avoid estrogen methods in other women. See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabHY5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   OB - OBESITY (BMI>30)   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabOB1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>OBESITY (BMI>30)</strong><strong></strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabOB5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabOB1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB2\">\n         <p>  Increased risk for birth defects, spontaneous abortion, pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes,  prematurity, perinatal death, maternal death, and childhood obesity. Offer specific strategies to decrease caloric intake and increase physical activity.</p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB3\">\n         <p> Screen for diabetes with 2 hr OGTT with a 75 gram  glucose load. Check blood pressure and manage appropriately. Provide nutrition and exercise counseling. Refer to <a href=\"http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.nih.gov/topic/Obesity</a></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB4\">\n         <p>Weight loss  medications should not be used during pregnancy.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabOB5\">\n         <p>All methods considered safe </p>\n  </div> <!-- end of tabOB5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n<!--   RD - Renal Disease   --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Renal Disease</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel to achieve optimal control (serum Cr &lt;1.4 mg/dl) of condition prior to conception. Discuss potential life-threatening risks during pregnancy. After transplant, wait 12-18 mo. And until comorbid risk factors under control (no or minimal proteinuria, absence or well-controlled HTN, stable serum Cr &lt;1.4, no graft rejection).  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD3\">\n         <p>  Consult with renal specialist.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD4\">\n         <p>ACE inhibitors  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabRD5\">\n         <p> See ACOG ref* for details. </p>\n      </div> <!-- end of tabRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SD  - Seizure Disorder--->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Seizure Disorder</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD2\">\n         <p>Counsel on potential effects of seizures and  seizure medications on pregnancy outcomes.  Counsel to take 4 mg folic acid per day at least 1 month prior to conception.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD3\">\n         <p> Whenever possible, monotherapy in the lowest therapeutic dose should be prescribed. </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD4\">\n         <p> Valproic Acid (DepakoteÂ®) </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n     </div> <!-- end of tabSD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n </div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   SLE - SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis    --->\n \n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabSLE1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>SLE & Rheumatoid Arthritis</strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabSLE5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabSLE1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE2\">\n         <p>  Disease should be in good control prior to pregnancy. </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE3\">\n         <p>Evaluate renal function and for end-organ disease.  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE4\">\n         <p>Cyclophosphamide   </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabSLE5\">\n        <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabSLE5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   TYD - Thyroid Disease   --->\n   \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTYD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thyroid Disease</strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTYD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTYD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD2\">\n         <p> Proper dosage of thyroid medication prior to conception for normal fetal development. Iodine intake 150 mcg per day.  </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD3\">\n         <p>  TSH < 3.0 and normal free T4 prior to pregnancy.  </p>\n    </p></div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD4\">\n         <p>   Radioactive iodine </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTYD5\">\n         <p>All methods  considered safe.</p>\n   </div> <!-- end of tabTYD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n<!--   TRD   --->\n  \n  <div class=\"tabbable\"> <!-- Only required for left/right tabs -->\n   <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs\">\n       <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#tabTRD1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" ><strong>Thromboembolic Disease </strong><strong> </strong></a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD2\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Counsel</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD3\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Test</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD4\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraindicated Medications</a></li>\n       <li><a href=\"#tabTRD5\" data-toggle=\"tab\">Contraception</a></li>\n   </ul>\n  <div class=\"tab-content\">\n    <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tabTRD1\">\n      \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD2\">\n         <p>Counsel regarding risk for venous thromboembolism during pregnancy and  postpartum.   </p>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD3\">\n         <p> Patient with history of venous thromboembolism: test for inherited thrombophillias and  antiphoshpholipid syndrome  </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD4\">\n         <p> Coumadin beyond 6   weeks GA </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tabTRD5\">\n         <p>See ACOG ref* for details.  </p>\n </div> <!-- end of tabTRD5 -->\n  </div>  <!--  end of tab-content   -->\n</div> <!-- end of tabbable  -->\n\n\n*ACOG Committee Opinion #505 Understanding and Using the U.S. Medical Eligibility Criteria for Contraceptive Useâ€ \n<a href=\"http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010\">http://www.acog.org/Resources_And_Publications/Committee_Opinions/Committee_on_Gynecologic_Practice/Understanding_and_Using_the_US_Medical_Eligibility_Criteria_for_Contraceptive_Use_2010</a>   This document should not be construed as dictating an exclusive course of treatment or procedure to be followed.\nVersion 2                                                                                                                                         1/17/2013','test icc guidlines','','inherit','closed','closed','','419-revision-v1','','','2013-08-15 11:04:42','2013-08-15 16:04:42','',419,'http://peace-p.org/419-revision-114/',0,'revision','',0),(716,4,'2013-10-10 09:26:34','2013-10-10 14:26:34','','Preeclampsia',' Approximately 7 to 10% of all pregnancies are complicated by hypertensive disease, 70% of which are gestational hypertension-preeclampsia related and 30% are due to chronic hypertension. (Sibai, 2010b) In the past, elevated blood pressure of more than 30 mm Hg systolic or more than 15 mm Hg diastolic above the patientâ€™s baseline was used to diagnose preeclampsia , however, this definition has not been shown to be a good prognostic indicator and is no longer recommended. (Report of the National High Blood Pressure Education Program Working Group on High Blood Pressure in Pregnancy,2000).Â  Although no longer considered diagnostic of preeclampsia, women demonstrating elevations of this magnitude should be carefully monitored for worsening High blood pressure in pregnancy is classified by four categories:','publish','closed','closed','','preeclampsia','','','2013-11-11 10:58:48','2013-11-11 16:58:48','',0,'http://peace-p.org/?post_type=gui